Package: DraftScoriverse
Title: Unified Framework For Extracting Predictions And Evaluating Models Using Proper Scoring Rules 
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Juan", "Jauanda", , "juanjayaj@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a consistent and automated framework for generating probabilistic predictions and evaluating models using proper scoring rules. Supports a wide range of model types, from classical statistical models to machine learning algorithms, through a unified API. Designed to assist data scientists and business decision-makers by incorporating predictive uncertainty and offering robust, probabilistically-sound evaluation metrics.
